<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF726ACDF81E937316C8BC11" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF726ACDF81E937316C8BC11" blockId="137.[2017,2610,1164,1592]" lastBlockId="137.[1399,2610,1598,3485]" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">
See 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF7D6937316E6BE79" authorityName="Horsfield" authorityYear="1824" box="[2090,2278,1322,1355]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hardwickii">K. hardwickii</taxonomicName>
. Current distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF7F3930B1686BE41" box="[2063,2182,1362,1395]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="furva">K. furva</taxonomicName>
is still uncertain and might be more expansive in South-east Asia or less expansive in South Asia. Specimens throughout 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF726ACDF769939116EABEDB" box="[2197,2282,1480,1513]" name="China" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">China</collectingCountry>
that were thought to represent 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF78993A91726BD23" authorityName="Horsfield" authorityYear="1824" box="[2165,2342,1520,1553]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hardwickii">K. hardwickii</taxonomicName>
and from 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF726ACDF63B93A9142FBD23" box="[2503,2607,1520,1553]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">Hainan</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF726ACDF7DC904E1682BD0A" box="[2080,2178,1559,1592]" name="Taiwan" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
islands that were identified as 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDFA8190671BFFBD6D" box="[1405,1535,1598,1631]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="titania">K. titania</taxonomicName>
are now considered to be 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF877906719FEBD6D" box="[1931,2046,1598,1631]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="furva">K. furva</taxonomicName>
, and its distribution has recently been shown to unequivocally extend south to 
<geoCoordinate id="A1A05039FF726ACDF833903C1620BDB4" box="[1999,2080,1637,1670]" degrees="18" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" precision="55555" value="18.0">18° N</geoCoordinate>
in 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF726ACDF7A8903C16CCBDB4" box="[2132,2252,1637,1670]" name="Vietnam" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
and west to eastern 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF726ACDF5FC903C1BA8BD9C" name="Nepal" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">Nepal</collectingCountry>
. Specimens form north-western 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF726ACDF88290D419C8BD9C" box="[1918,1992,1677,1710]" name="India" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">India</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF726ACDF7E890D41688BD9C" box="[2068,2184,1677,1710]" name="Pakistan" pageId="137" pageNumber="897">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
have not yet been compared with other members of the 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF90690ED197EBDE7" authorityName="Horsfield" authorityYear="1824" box="[1786,1918,1716,1749]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hardwickii">hardwickii</taxonomicName>
species group and are tentatively included under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDFA8190851BEBBDCF" box="[1405,1515,1756,1789]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="furva">K. furva</taxonomicName>
. Genetically, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF95890851912BDCF" box="[1700,1810,1756,1789]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="furva">K. furva</taxonomicName>
appearsto be sister to a clade including 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF6B4908517D6BDCF" authorityName="G. S. Miller" authorityYear="1906" box="[2376,2518,1756,1789]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="depressa">K. depressa</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF61890851BF0BC11" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="kachinensis">K. kachinensis</taxonomicName>
, and true South-east Asian 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF726ACDF88C915B161DBC11" authorityName="Horsfield" authorityYear="1824" box="[1904,2077,1794,1827]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="137" pageNumber="897" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hardwickii">K. hardwickii</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
